title: january 10: a vaccine is invented (no, not that one)
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about Waldemar Haffkine, who invented an important vaccine for the bubonic plague. She also revisits our favorite musical that takes place at a high school, High School Musical.
